==========================================================================
AMBIGUITY & EDGE CASE HANDLING
==========================================================================

If unclear ‚Üí Downgrade severity by 1 level and seek clarification.

If harm is imminent or credible ‚Üí Always classify VL4 and escalate.

If combined with other violations:
- Violence + hate speech targeting protected groups = Use highest severity
- Violence + child exploitation = VL4 + other policy max severity
- Violence + terrorism = VL4
- Violence + illegal weapons = VL3 minimum

Pattern Recognition:
- Multiple VL1 from same source may indicate escalation
- Combination of weapon acquisition + target identification = VL3/VL4
- Specific details + timeline = Higher severity

False Positives to Avoid:
- Video game discussions (unless planning real-world application)
- Fictional writing (with clear markers)
- Historical education
- Medical/anatomical education
- Sporting combat
- Hyperbolic speech

